com.fortify.client.ssc.connection

  • Packages that use com.fortify.client.ssc.connection 
    Package Description
    com.fortify.bugtracker.common.ssc.connection
    This package contains single class for instantiating SSCAuthenticatingRestConnection instances based on connection properties provided by a given Context instance.
    com.fortify.client.ssc.api  
    com.fortify.client.ssc.api.query
    The SSCEntityQuery class in this package is the main class for performing SSC-related queries.
    com.fortify.client.ssc.api.query.builder
    This package provides various builder classes used to configure REST queries and building a corresponding SSCEntityQuery instance.
    com.fortify.client.ssc.connection
    This package provides the main functionality for accessing the SSC REST API.
